{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01FeWakoYxtM27fuUZa2d3RT","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Excellent! Now I have all the information. Let me compile a comprehensive summary of the codebase for building the user profile page.\n\n## Complete Codebase Analysis for User Profile Page\n\nI've thoroughly explored the ThemeDrops codebase. Here's a comprehensive summary of all the key files and patterns you'll need to build the user profile page:\n\n---\n\n## KEY FILES AND FULL CONTENTS\n\n### 1. **Theme Detail Page** - `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/src/app/theme/[slug]/page.tsx`\n(Already provided above - 737 lines)\n\n**Key patterns:**\n- Uses `useParams()` for dynamic routing with `[slug]` segments\n- Header layout: Logo, navigation buttons (CreateThemeLink, AuthControls)\n- Data fetching: `useQuery()` for theme data, author info, stars, comments\n- Mutation patterns: `useMutation()` for toggleStar, createComment, updateTheme, removeTheme\n- Edit mode with inline state management (editName, editDescription, editColors, editFonts)\n- Authorization: Owner detection via `currentUser._id === theme.authorId`\n- Error handling with try/catch blocks\n- Form submission patterns for comments\n\n---\n\n### 2. **Homepage** - `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/src/app/page.tsx`\n(Already provided above - 365 lines)\n\n**Key patterns:**\n- Hero header with animated gradient backdrop\n- Search functionality with debouncing (300ms)\n- ThemeCard component that displays:\n  - Color palette strip at top\n  - Theme name, author name (displayName ?? username)\n  - Description (2-line clamp)\n  - Mini color swatches\n  - Star count\n  - Preview strip showing background/foreground colors\n- Pagination with `usePaginatedQuery()` and \"Load more\" button\n- Loading skeletons (CardSkeleton)\n- Empty states for no themes and no search results\n\n---\n\n### 3. **User Queries** - `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/convex/users.ts`\n(Already provided above - 110 lines)\n\n**Key exports:**\n- `get({ id })` - Get user by ID (returns: _id, username, displayName, avatarUrl)\n- `getByUsername({ username })` - Query with index \"by_username\"\n- `getCurrentUser()` - Get authenticated user via tokenIdentifier\n- `updateProfile({ displayName, bio, avatarUrl })` - Mutation to update user\n- `ensureUser()` - Creates user on first login, auto-generates unique username\n\n**Important:** User has optional fields: bio, avatarUrl, displayName, username\n\n---\n\n### 4. **Stars Queries** - `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/convex/stars.ts`\n(Already provided above - 105 lines)\n\n**Key exports:**\n- `isStarred({ themeId })` - Check if current user starred a theme\n- `toggle({ themeId })` - Toggle star (returns boolean)\n- `getStarredThemes({ userId })` - Get all themes starred by a user (takes 50, respects privacy)\n\n**Privacy pattern:** Filters out private themes unless viewer is author\n\n---\n\n### 5. **Create Page** - `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/src/app/create/page.tsx`\n(Already provided above - 337 lines)\n\n**Key patterns:**\n- Check `isAuthenticated` before rendering form\n- Form sections: Details, Visibility (toggle), Colors, Live Preview, Fonts\n- Color fields configuration with defaults\n- Font inputs for sans/serif/mono\n- Form submission with error handling\n- LivePreview component showing button colors and text\n\n---\n\n### 6. **Database Schema** - `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/convex/schema.ts`\n(Already provided above - 73 lines)\n\n**Users table:**\n```typescript\nusers: {\n  // Auth fields (from @convex-dev/auth)\n  name, image, email, emailVerificationTime, phone, phoneVerificationTime, isAnonymous\n  // Custom fields\n  username: string (indexed \"by_username\")\n  displayName, bio, avatarUrl, tokenIdentifier (indexed \"by_token\")\n}\n```\n\n**Themes table:**\n```typescript\nthemes: {\n  name, slug (indexed \"by_slug\"), description, authorId (indexed \"by_author\")\n  forkedFromId, isPublic, starCount (indexed \"by_star_count\")\n  colors: { background, foreground, primary, secondary, accent, muted }\n  fonts: { sans, serif, mono } (optional)\n}\n```\n\n**Stars table:**\n```typescript\nstars: {\n  userId, themeId\n  indexes: \"by_user_and_theme\", \"by_theme\"\n}\n```\n\n**Comments table:**\n```typescript\ncomments: {\n  userId, themeId, body\n  indexes: \"by_theme\", \"by_user\"\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 7. **Theme Mutations** - `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/convex/themes.ts`\n(Already provided above - 312 lines)\n\n**Key exports:**\n- `list()` - Paginated public themes ordered by star count\n- `getBySlug({ slug })` - With privacy check\n- `getByAuthor({ authorId })` - Returns all themes if owner, only public if viewer\n- `getBasicInfo({ id })` - Returns { name, slug } only\n- `search({ name })` - Search public themes (takes 40, returns 20)\n- `create()` - Creates theme with slug generation\n- `update({ id, name, ... })` - Updates and regenerates slug if name changes\n- `remove()` - Deletes theme and all associated stars/comments\n- `fork({ id })` - Creates copy with \"(fork)\" suffix, marked private\n\n---\n\n### 8. **Comments Queries** - `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/convex/comments.ts`\n(Already provided above - 97 lines)\n\n**Key exports:**\n- `listByTheme({ themeId })` - Returns comments with author info (username, displayName, avatarUrl)\n- `create({ themeId, body })` - Create comment\n- `remove({ id })` - Delete comment (only author can)\n\n---\n\n### 9. **Components**\n\n#### AuthControls - `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/src/app/components/AuthControls.tsx`\n(Already provided above - 59 lines)\n\n**Pattern:**\n- Shows username/displayName when authenticated\n- Sign in/out buttons\n- Calls `ensureUser()` mutation on auth\n- Uses `useAuthActions()` from @convex-dev/auth/react\n\n#### CreateThemeLink - `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/src/app/components/CreateThemeLink.tsx`\n(Already provided above - 20 lines)\n\n**Pattern:**\n- Only shows when authenticated\n- Simple Link to /create\n\n#### AuthModal - `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/src/app/components/AuthModal.tsx`\n(Already provided above - 138 lines)\n\n**Pattern:**\n- Sign in/Sign up tabs\n- Uses `signIn(\"password\", formData)` from useAuthActions\n- FormData with email, password, flow (\"signIn\" or \"signUp\")\n- Modal backdrop with click-to-close\n\n---\n\n### 10. **Layout & Providers**\n\n#### Root Layout - `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/src/app/layout.tsx`\n(Already provided above - 37 lines)\n\n**Pattern:**\n- Wraps children with `ConvexClientProvider`\n- Uses Geist fonts from Google Fonts\n- HTML lang=\"en\", body with min-h-full\n\n#### Providers - `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/src/app/providers.tsx`\n(Already provided above - 16 lines)\n\n**Pattern:**\n- Creates ConvexReactClient with `process.env.NEXT_PUBLIC_CONVEX_URL`\n- Wraps app with `ConvexAuthProvider`\n\n#### Globals CSS - `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/src/app/globals.css`\n(Already provided above - 27 lines)\n\n**Pattern:**\n- Uses Tailwind CSS\n- Custom CSS variables for theme colors\n- Supports light/dark mode\n\n---\n\n## ARCHITECTURAL PATTERNS TO FOLLOW FOR USER PROFILE PAGE\n\n### 1. **Page Structure**\n```\n/app/src/app/profile/[username]/page.tsx\n- Header (ThemeDrops logo, AuthControls)\n- User info section (avatar, displayName, username, bio)\n- Tabs/sections: My Themes, Starred Themes\n- Theme grid with ThemeCard components\n```\n\n### 2. **Data Fetching**\n```typescript\nconst user = useQuery(api.users.getByUsername, { username });\nconst userThemes = useQuery(api.themes.getByAuthor, user ? { authorId: user._id } : \"skip\");\nconst starredThemes = useQuery(api.stars.getStarredThemes, user ? { userId: user._id } : \"skip\");\nconst currentUser = useQuery(api.users.getCurrentUser);\n```\n\n### 3. **Authorization Pattern**\n```typescript\nconst isOwnProfile = currentUser && user && currentUser._id === user._id;\n// Show edit button only if isOwnProfile\n```\n\n### 4. **Edit Profile Pattern** (similar to theme editing)\n```typescript\nconst [editing, setEditing] = useState(false);\nconst [editDisplayName, setEditDisplayName] = useState(\"\");\nconst [editBio, setEditBio] = useState(\"\");\nconst updateProfile = useMutation(api.users.updateProfile);\n```\n\n### 5. **Navigation Pattern**\nAll pages use header with:\n```tsx\n<a href=\"/\" className=\"text-lg font-bold tracking-tight\">ThemeDrops</a>\n<CreateThemeLink />\n<AuthControls />\n```\n\n### 6. **Author Name Rendering Pattern**\n```typescript\n{author?.displayName ?? author?.username}\n// Or for optional author:\n{author && (author.displayName ?? author.username)}\n```\n\n### 7. **Styling Pattern**\n- Tailwind CSS with gray color palette (gray-50 to gray-900)\n- Border: `border border-gray-200`\n- Rounded: `rounded-lg`, `rounded-xl`, `rounded-2xl`\n- Spacing: `gap-3`, `gap-4`, `gap-6`, `space-y-4`, `px-4`, `py-2`, etc.\n- Hover states: `hover:bg-gray-50`, `hover:text-gray-700`\n- Transitions: `transition-colors`, `transition-all`\n\n### 8. **Loading States**\nUse `undefined` vs `null` distinction:\n- `undefined` = loading\n- `null` = not found/null result\n- Show loading skeleton while `=== undefined`\n\n---\n\n## CONVEX QUERIES YOU'LL NEED TO ADD\n\nTo fully support the profile page, you may want to add to `convex/users.ts`:\n\n```typescript\nexport const getByIdWithStats = query({\n  args: { id: v.id(\"users\") },\n  handler: async (ctx, args) => {\n    const user = await ctx.db.get(args.id);\n    if (!user) return null;\n    \n    const themeCount = await ctx.db\n      .query(\"themes\")\n      .withIndex(\"by_author\", (q) => q.eq(\"authorId\", args.id))\n      .count();\n    \n    return {\n      _id: user._id,\n      username: user.username,\n      displayName: user.displayName,\n      bio: user.bio,\n      avatarUrl: user.avatarUrl,\n      themeCount,\n    };\n  },\n});\n```\n\n---\n\n## FILE PATHS SUMMARY\n\n**Page files:**\n- `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/src/app/page.tsx` - Homepage\n- `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/src/app/theme/[slug]/page.tsx` - Theme detail\n- `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/src/app/create/page.tsx` - Create theme\n- `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/src/app/layout.tsx` - Root layout\n- `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/src/app/providers.tsx` - Auth provider setup\n\n**Component files:**\n- `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/src/app/components/AuthControls.tsx`\n- `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/src/app/components/CreateThemeLink.tsx`\n- `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/src/app/components/AuthModal.tsx`\n\n**Backend files:**\n- `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/convex/schema.ts` - Database schema\n- `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/convex/users.ts` - User queries/mutations\n- `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/convex/stars.ts` - Star queries/mutations\n- `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/convex/themes.ts` - Theme queries/mutations\n- `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/convex/comments.ts` - Comment queries/mutations\n\n**Styling:**\n- `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/src/app/globals.css` - Global styles\n\n---\n\nThis should give you everything you need to build the user profile page! The patterns are consistent across the codebase, so follow the same header structure, authorization checks, and component patterns you see in the theme detail page and homepage."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"2ee1c275-4822-470d-95d7-c91f2b4b25ff","uuid":"c54b110c-0af6-4e46-9e61-e71e3b7fd0d1","timestamp":"2026-03-28T00:03:20.970Z","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Explore the codebase at /Users/matt/code/themedrops/app to understand the existing patterns. I need to build a user profile page. Please find and return the FULL contents of these files:\n\n1. app/src/app/theme/[slug]/page.tsx - the theme detail page (to understand page patterns, header, layout)\n2. app/src/app/page.tsx - the homepage (to understand ThemeCard and author name rendering)\n3. Any convex files related to users and stars queries (users.ts, stars.ts) - to understand the API\n4. app/src/app/theme/create/page.tsx - to understand the create page pattern\n\nAlso check if there are any shared components or layout files I should know about. Be very thorough - return full file contents for all files found.","agentId":"a5af07c86d2f4b4cd","agentType":"Explore","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Excellent! Now I have all the information. Let me compile a comprehensive summary of the codebase for building the user profile page.\n\n## Complete Codebase Analysis for User Profile Page\n\nI've thoroughly explored the ThemeDrops codebase. Here's a comprehensive summary of all the key files and patterns you'll need to build the user profile page:\n\n---\n\n## KEY FILES AND FULL CONTENTS\n\n### 1. **Theme Detail Page** - `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/src/app/theme/[slug]/page.tsx`\n(Already provided above - 737 lines)\n\n**Key patterns:**\n- Uses `useParams()` for dynamic routing with `[slug]` segments\n- Header layout: Logo, navigation buttons (CreateThemeLink, AuthControls)\n- Data fetching: `useQuery()` for theme data, author info, stars, comments\n- Mutation patterns: `useMutation()` for toggleStar, createComment, updateTheme, removeTheme\n- Edit mode with inline state management (editName, editDescription, editColors, editFonts)\n- Authorization: Owner detection via `currentUser._id === theme.authorId`\n- Error handling with try/catch blocks\n- Form submission patterns for comments\n\n---\n\n### 2. **Homepage** - `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/src/app/page.tsx`\n(Already provided above - 365 lines)\n\n**Key patterns:**\n- Hero header with animated gradient backdrop\n- Search functionality with debouncing (300ms)\n- ThemeCard component that displays:\n  - Color palette strip at top\n  - Theme name, author name (displayName ?? username)\n  - Description (2-line clamp)\n  - Mini color swatches\n  - Star count\n  - Preview strip showing background/foreground colors\n- Pagination with `usePaginatedQuery()` and \"Load more\" button\n- Loading skeletons (CardSkeleton)\n- Empty states for no themes and no search results\n\n---\n\n### 3. **User Queries** - `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/convex/users.ts`\n(Already provided above - 110 lines)\n\n**Key exports:**\n- `get({ id })` - Get user by ID (returns: _id, username, displayName, avatarUrl)\n- `getByUsername({ username })` - Query with index \"by_username\"\n- `getCurrentUser()` - Get authenticated user via tokenIdentifier\n- `updateProfile({ displayName, bio, avatarUrl })` - Mutation to update user\n- `ensureUser()` - Creates user on first login, auto-generates unique username\n\n**Important:** User has optional fields: bio, avatarUrl, displayName, username\n\n---\n\n### 4. **Stars Queries** - `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/convex/stars.ts`\n(Already provided above - 105 lines)\n\n**Key exports:**\n- `isStarred({ themeId })` - Check if current user starred a theme\n- `toggle({ themeId })` - Toggle star (returns boolean)\n- `getStarredThemes({ userId })` - Get all themes starred by a user (takes 50, respects privacy)\n\n**Privacy pattern:** Filters out private themes unless viewer is author\n\n---\n\n### 5. **Create Page** - `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/src/app/create/page.tsx`\n(Already provided above - 337 lines)\n\n**Key patterns:**\n- Check `isAuthenticated` before rendering form\n- Form sections: Details, Visibility (toggle), Colors, Live Preview, Fonts\n- Color fields configuration with defaults\n- Font inputs for sans/serif/mono\n- Form submission with error handling\n- LivePreview component showing button colors and text\n\n---\n\n### 6. **Database Schema** - `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/convex/schema.ts`\n(Already provided above - 73 lines)\n\n**Users table:**\n```typescript\nusers: {\n  // Auth fields (from @convex-dev/auth)\n  name, image, email, emailVerificationTime, phone, phoneVerificationTime, isAnonymous\n  // Custom fields\n  username: string (indexed \"by_username\")\n  displayName, bio, avatarUrl, tokenIdentifier (indexed \"by_token\")\n}\n```\n\n**Themes table:**\n```typescript\nthemes: {\n  name, slug (indexed \"by_slug\"), description, authorId (indexed \"by_author\")\n  forkedFromId, isPublic, starCount (indexed \"by_star_count\")\n  colors: { background, foreground, primary, secondary, accent, muted }\n  fonts: { sans, serif, mono } (optional)\n}\n```\n\n**Stars table:**\n```typescript\nstars: {\n  userId, themeId\n  indexes: \"by_user_and_theme\", \"by_theme\"\n}\n```\n\n**Comments table:**\n```typescript\ncomments: {\n  userId, themeId, body\n  indexes: \"by_theme\", \"by_user\"\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 7. **Theme Mutations** - `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/convex/themes.ts`\n(Already provided above - 312 lines)\n\n**Key exports:**\n- `list()` - Paginated public themes ordered by star count\n- `getBySlug({ slug })` - With privacy check\n- `getByAuthor({ authorId })` - Returns all themes if owner, only public if viewer\n- `getBasicInfo({ id })` - Returns { name, slug } only\n- `search({ name })` - Search public themes (takes 40, returns 20)\n- `create()` - Creates theme with slug generation\n- `update({ id, name, ... })` - Updates and regenerates slug if name changes\n- `remove()` - Deletes theme and all associated stars/comments\n- `fork({ id })` - Creates copy with \"(fork)\" suffix, marked private\n\n---\n\n### 8. **Comments Queries** - `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/convex/comments.ts`\n(Already provided above - 97 lines)\n\n**Key exports:**\n- `listByTheme({ themeId })` - Returns comments with author info (username, displayName, avatarUrl)\n- `create({ themeId, body })` - Create comment\n- `remove({ id })` - Delete comment (only author can)\n\n---\n\n### 9. **Components**\n\n#### AuthControls - `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/src/app/components/AuthControls.tsx`\n(Already provided above - 59 lines)\n\n**Pattern:**\n- Shows username/displayName when authenticated\n- Sign in/out buttons\n- Calls `ensureUser()` mutation on auth\n- Uses `useAuthActions()` from @convex-dev/auth/react\n\n#### CreateThemeLink - `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/src/app/components/CreateThemeLink.tsx`\n(Already provided above - 20 lines)\n\n**Pattern:**\n- Only shows when authenticated\n- Simple Link to /create\n\n#### AuthModal - `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/src/app/components/AuthModal.tsx`\n(Already provided above - 138 lines)\n\n**Pattern:**\n- Sign in/Sign up tabs\n- Uses `signIn(\"password\", formData)` from useAuthActions\n- FormData with email, password, flow (\"signIn\" or \"signUp\")\n- Modal backdrop with click-to-close\n\n---\n\n### 10. **Layout & Providers**\n\n#### Root Layout - `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/src/app/layout.tsx`\n(Already provided above - 37 lines)\n\n**Pattern:**\n- Wraps children with `ConvexClientProvider`\n- Uses Geist fonts from Google Fonts\n- HTML lang=\"en\", body with min-h-full\n\n#### Providers - `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/src/app/providers.tsx`\n(Already provided above - 16 lines)\n\n**Pattern:**\n- Creates ConvexReactClient with `process.env.NEXT_PUBLIC_CONVEX_URL`\n- Wraps app with `ConvexAuthProvider`\n\n#### Globals CSS - `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/src/app/globals.css`\n(Already provided above - 27 lines)\n\n**Pattern:**\n- Uses Tailwind CSS\n- Custom CSS variables for theme colors\n- Supports light/dark mode\n\n---\n\n## ARCHITECTURAL PATTERNS TO FOLLOW FOR USER PROFILE PAGE\n\n### 1. **Page Structure**\n```\n/app/src/app/profile/[username]/page.tsx\n- Header (ThemeDrops logo, AuthControls)\n- User info section (avatar, displayName, username, bio)\n- Tabs/sections: My Themes, Starred Themes\n- Theme grid with ThemeCard components\n```\n\n### 2. **Data Fetching**\n```typescript\nconst user = useQuery(api.users.getByUsername, { username });\nconst userThemes = useQuery(api.themes.getByAuthor, user ? { authorId: user._id } : \"skip\");\nconst starredThemes = useQuery(api.stars.getStarredThemes, user ? { userId: user._id } : \"skip\");\nconst currentUser = useQuery(api.users.getCurrentUser);\n```\n\n### 3. **Authorization Pattern**\n```typescript\nconst isOwnProfile = currentUser && user && currentUser._id === user._id;\n// Show edit button only if isOwnProfile\n```\n\n### 4. **Edit Profile Pattern** (similar to theme editing)\n```typescript\nconst [editing, setEditing] = useState(false);\nconst [editDisplayName, setEditDisplayName] = useState(\"\");\nconst [editBio, setEditBio] = useState(\"\");\nconst updateProfile = useMutation(api.users.updateProfile);\n```\n\n### 5. **Navigation Pattern**\nAll pages use header with:\n```tsx\n<a href=\"/\" className=\"text-lg font-bold tracking-tight\">ThemeDrops</a>\n<CreateThemeLink />\n<AuthControls />\n```\n\n### 6. **Author Name Rendering Pattern**\n```typescript\n{author?.displayName ?? author?.username}\n// Or for optional author:\n{author && (author.displayName ?? author.username)}\n```\n\n### 7. **Styling Pattern**\n- Tailwind CSS with gray color palette (gray-50 to gray-900)\n- Border: `border border-gray-200`\n- Rounded: `rounded-lg`, `rounded-xl`, `rounded-2xl`\n- Spacing: `gap-3`, `gap-4`, `gap-6`, `space-y-4`, `px-4`, `py-2`, etc.\n- Hover states: `hover:bg-gray-50`, `hover:text-gray-700`\n- Transitions: `transition-colors`, `transition-all`\n\n### 8. **Loading States**\nUse `undefined` vs `null` distinction:\n- `undefined` = loading\n- `null` = not found/null result\n- Show loading skeleton while `=== undefined`\n\n---\n\n## CONVEX QUERIES YOU'LL NEED TO ADD\n\nTo fully support the profile page, you may want to add to `convex/users.ts`:\n\n```typescript\nexport const getByIdWithStats = query({\n  args: { id: v.id(\"users\") },\n  handler: async (ctx, args) => {\n    const user = await ctx.db.get(args.id);\n    if (!user) return null;\n    \n    const themeCount = await ctx.db\n      .query(\"themes\")\n      .withIndex(\"by_author\", (q) => q.eq(\"authorId\", args.id))\n      .count();\n    \n    return {\n      _id: user._id,\n      username: user.username,\n      displayName: user.displayName,\n      bio: user.bio,\n      avatarUrl: user.avatarUrl,\n      themeCount,\n    };\n  },\n});\n```\n\n---\n\n## FILE PATHS SUMMARY\n\n**Page files:**\n- `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/src/app/page.tsx` - Homepage\n- `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/src/app/theme/[slug]/page.tsx` - Theme detail\n- `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/src/app/create/page.tsx` - Create theme\n- `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/src/app/layout.tsx` - Root layout\n- `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/src/app/providers.tsx` - Auth provider setup\n\n**Component files:**\n- `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/src/app/components/AuthControls.tsx`\n- `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/src/app/components/CreateThemeLink.tsx`\n- `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/src/app/components/AuthModal.tsx`\n\n**Backend files:**\n- `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/convex/schema.ts` - Database schema\n- `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/convex/users.ts` - User queries/mutations\n- `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/convex/stars.ts` - Star queries/mutations\n- `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/convex/themes.ts` - Theme queries/mutations\n- `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/convex/comments.ts` - Comment queries/mutations\n\n**Styling:**\n- `/Users/matt/code/themedrops/app/src/app/globals.css` - Global styles\n\n---\n\nThis should give you everything you need to build the user profile page! The patterns are consistent across the codebase, so follow the same header structure, authorization checks, and component patterns you see in the theme detail page and homepage."}],"totalDurationMs":47513,"totalTokens":57156,"totalToolUseCount":22,"usage":{"input_tokens":6,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2661,"cache_read_input_tokens":51130,"output_tokens":3359,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":2661},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
